model.name: keyStoreParameters
model.title: Key Store Parameters
model.description: Key store facility for cryptographic keys and certificates
model.label: security,configuration

type.description: The optional type of the key store to load. See Appendix A in the Java Cryptography Architecture Standard Algorithm Name Documentation for more information on standard names.

password.description: The optional password for reading/opening/verifying the key store

provider.description: The optional provider identifier for instantiating the key store

resource.description: The optional file path, class path resource, or URL of the resource used to load the key store

camelContextId.description: Id of CamelContext to use if there are multiple CamelContexts in the same JVM
